{"tid":1186483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平：經常愉快回憶與普京每一次交往","createTime":"2019-06-05T03:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T03:20:21.000Z","uid":241764,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ad16418d695ded57f5f6a6a7dda46170a2817d76","tid":1186483,"uid":241764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:14:09.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平應俄羅斯總統普京要求，今日（5日）起一連三日國事訪問俄羅斯。他周二（4日）接受俄羅斯多家傳媒訪問，被問及如何評價與普京的關係時表示，自己「經常愉快回憶與普京每一次交往」，形容普京是他「最好的知心朋友」。<br />\n<br />\n習近平表示，自己曾跟普京深入交流不少議題，既包括國際形勢、雙邊關係及治國理政，也涉及文學、藝術和運動等輕鬆愉快話題，「我們共同乘坐高鐵交流，一同觀看中俄青少年冰球友誼賽，在峇里島慶祝生日，在對方國家重要節日時通電話或致信函相互祝賀，我們還都被對方國家授予最高國家榮譽勳章&hellip;&hellip;普京總統是我交往最密切的外國同事，是我最好的知心朋友，我十分珍視同普京總統這份深厚的情誼」。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又強調，他與普京對當前世界大勢看法相近，在治理國家方面理念相通，肩負兩國各自發展振興的歷史責任，他願與普京保持密切交往，「共同引領兩國關係邁向更高水平，為中國和俄羅斯這兩個偉大國家發展繁榮，為兩國人民幸福安寧不懈努力」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190605/s00004/1559698588291/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E7%B6%93%E5%B8%B8%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E8%88%87%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190605%2Fs00004%2F1559698588291%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%2584%2589%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2586%25B6%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25AF%258F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25BE%2580&d=bqe6r6CGoyJNILHzVVCKLz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=b29bb551\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25B2%25B8%2Farticle%2F20190605%2Fs00004%2F1559698588291%2F%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E6%2584%2589%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2586%25B6%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%2599%25AE%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E6%25AF%258F%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25AC%25A1%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E5%25BE%2580&h=f34f739c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20190605/s00004/1559698588291/%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E7%B6%93%E5%B8%B8%E6%84%89%E5%BF%AB%E5%9B%9E%E6%86%B6%E8%88%87%E6%99%AE%E4%BA%AC%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%80%E6%AC%A1%E4%BA%A4%E5%BE%80</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4f2642eea75d76d96c907258949c19a69682d0","tid":1186483,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:16:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5424df86bb5a5166106906c2119a4e3045e724","tid":1186483,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:16:31.000Z","msg":"Gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa8f361cf41e599704f190f4824490591400386","tid":1186483,"uid":118623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:18:14.000Z","msg":"房租是一次性交易的.jpg"},{"pid":"511ef3fbc9f09e9f25f02d4b8c692c2eb31c9ede","tid":1186483,"uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:18:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DX_KpQfVMAEI183.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDX_KpQfVMAEI183.jpg&h=ca31fc0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a9a92fe1587065d34197eba065732e45ecd0233","tid":1186483,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-05T03:18:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/03/07/jJo25t.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F03%2F07%2FjJo25t.png&h=47352557&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd595af5b071596a00b6ac372f91f8d41da446bf",